ADDITIONAL TERMS FOR REDUCTRAI

The following additional terms apply to ReductrAI:

A. OPEN CORE MODEL

This License applies to the ReductrAI Agent (the "Open Source Component"):
- apps/binary/ (Go binary agent)
- Command-line interface
- Telemetry ingestion
- Local storage (DuckDB)
- Anomaly detection
- Compression algorithms

The following components are NOT covered by this License and remain
proprietary to ReductrAI:
- Cloud Dashboard (app.reductrai.com)
- AI Relay Service
- Managed LLM infrastructure
- Commercial support

B. LOCAL-ONLY MODE

You may run the Open Source Component in local-only mode without a license:
- Full telemetry ingestion and storage
- Local anomaly detection
- Integration with your own LLM (Ollama, vLLM, OpenAI, etc.)
- No data sent to ReductrAI cloud

For cloud features (Dashboard, AI Relay), a commercial license is required.

C. CONTRIBUTION GUIDELINES

Contributions to the Open Source Component are welcome under the terms of
this License. By contributing, you agree to license your contributions
under the same terms.

